---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'; import HeroLattice from '../components/HeroLattice.astro'; import ResearchCard from '../components/ResearchCard.astro'; import Pipeline from '../components/Pipeline.astro'; import {research,pending} from '../content';
---
<BaseLayout title="尖端材料及製程實驗室" lang="zh-Hant"><section class="hero"><div data-reveal><span class="eyebrow">NCKU Mechanical Engineering · AMPL</span><h1>尖端材料<br/>及製程實驗室</h1><p class="subhead">Advanced Material and Processing Lab</p><p>以綠色合成、循環經濟、奈米材料與表面工程為軸，串連材料設計、製程、表徵及應用的研究視野。</p><div class="hero-actions"><a class="button primary" href="#research">探索研究領域</a><a class="button secondary" href="/join-us">加入我們</a></div></div><HeroLattice/></section><section class="identity"><div><h2>研究識別<br/>Research identity</h2><p>從永續資源到功能材料，從微觀結構到實際應用；以精確的材料與製程研究，回應工程、環境與生醫需求。</p></div></section><section id="research"><div class="section-head"><h2>研究領域</h2><p>以跨尺度的材料思維，連結資源循環、結構設計、界面工程與製程最佳化。</p></div><div class="research-grid">{research.map(([english,chinese,description],index)=><ResearchCard {english} {chinese} {description} {index}/>)}</div></section><section><div class="section-head"><h2>材料至應用</h2><p>從原料選擇到材料行為與應用效能，形成可被理解、驗證與持續優化的研究流程。</p></div><Pipeline/></section><section><div class="section-head"><h2>研究亮點與出版品</h2><p>代表性成果將在經確認後公布。</p></div><div class="placeholder"><b>SELECTED HIGHLIGHTS</b>{pending['zh-Hant']}</div></section><section class="join"><div><div><span class="eyebrow">Join AMPL</span><h2>以材料研究，參與更好的未來。</h2><p>歡迎對材料製程、奈米材料、表面工程、摩擦學與模擬設計有興趣的學生加入。</p></div><a class="button primary" href="/join-us">加入我們</a></div></section></BaseLayout>
